textBox.richText: Last night I had a blast recording for Cozmic Danger. We also laid down some sexy tracks for Sex Copter to use. Nathan and I both are into the idea of processing the shit out of the vocals to give them a Cozmic vibe. I can’t wait to hear how they sound. We recorded in the basement (soon to be studio) of their new place, which is really legit. I especially like the wood paneling on the walls. Combined with the black light, it gives the space a sexy funky retro feel. I think we should make a vid together soon any ideas? www.myspace.com/cozmiccollisions
